    "unit_id": "p13_g01",
    "unit_mode": "semantic_group",
    "slot_count": 3,
    "source_text": "友邦保險是客戶誠可信賴的夥伴，讓客戶在關注財務安全和家庭保障時仍可安心無憂。儘管2019冠狀病毒病大\n流行的影響深遠，但我衷心感謝我們的員工、代理和合作夥伴在適應新工作方式並確保為客戶提供無間斷的支援\n時，展現靈活應變的能力和克盡己職的精神。",
    "current_translation": "AIA is a trusted partner our customers can rely on, providing them with peace of mind as they focus on their financial security and family protection. Despite the far-reaching impact of the COVID-19 pandemic, I am deeply grateful to our employees, agents and partners for demonstrating flexibility and dedication in adapting to new ways of working and ensuring uninterrupted support to our customers."
  },
